ygData.messageBody:
WHO: "Skel" the 21th lvl Gnome necromancer
WHERE:Eci
WHEN: 8pm-1130pm est


I am an L21 Gnome Necromancer looking for a group to adventure with. I have been soloing for a long time and advanceing fast. But as everyone knows, it gets harder at higher lvls, and it is not as much fun alone either.

My characters name is Skel

If you are in the 20-28th lvl range and could use another person to group with give me a /tell I am a team player and most of my good friends are way high lvl because they play tons more. I don't know where they get the time. If you want to just try me in the group that is fine too! :-) Give me a /tell

I play from 8Eastern until about midnight everynight.

Thanks
